Traffic Morphing Examples

Shift4 originally proposed that NVR pay Shift4 the following for the HPS traffic:

TRANSACTION       TRANSACTION TYPE                SWITCH FEE          NETWORK ACCESS
TYPE

Credit            Auth/Capture(Sale)               $.0395                   $ .017

Credit            Credit(Return)                   $.0395                   $ .017
Credit            Void                            $.0395
Credit            Force Credit *                  $.0395                   $ .017
Debit             Auth/Capture(Sale)               $.0395                   $ .017

Debit             Credit(Return)                   $.0395                   $ .017

Debit             Void                            $.0395
 
NVR requested the following for the HPS traffic:
TRANSACTION       TRANSACTION TYPE                SWITCH FEE          NETWORK ACCESS
TYPE

Credit            Auth/Capture(Sale)               $.015                   $ .017
Credit            Credit(Return)                   $.015                   $ .017
Credit            Void                            $.015

Credit            Force Credit *                  $.015                   $.017
Debit             Auth/Capture(Sale)               $.015                    $ .017
Debit             Credit(Return)                   $ .015                   $ .017

Debit             Void                            $.015
 

* Force Credits are a problem. All other transactions are fine.
